Job Descriptions:

  Loading / unloading of equipment   
  Installation &amp; assembly of equipment
  Carry out simple mechanical works like grinding / cutting / drilling
  Carry out minor cleaning works
  Assist engineer and supervisor on other technical and manual works


Job Requirements:

  Willing to work in construction and waste treament plant
  Able to work at dusty and noisy environment
  Know how to operate tools like grinder, cutter, electric drill, etc.
  Physically fit
  Ensure workplace safety practices 
  Able to work long hour and overtime
  Able to converse and understand English
